"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94b56f0b709140abb22f16116e9bd332f7bb52dd","tid":1762400,"uid":51134,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:37:56.000Z","msg":"馨竹難書好似係形容一個人啲做到衰嘢多到數唔曬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手寫會更有溫度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:59:54.000Z","msg":"有用馨竹難書咩篇野？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:12:40.000Z","msg":"希望到時佢睇完封信，唔會屌柒我呢個老豆長氣無聊啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實在太多太多野想講佢知，罄竹難書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:14:18.000Z","msg":"我中文廢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5571aecef6f7f880eb0871572a7ad1dc151b0726","tid":1762400,"uid":273991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:19:09.000Z","msg":"新手爸爸加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f1f258d14300e124863db8f1434f1baa342caf","tid":1762400,"uid":38305,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T13:42:20.000Z","msg":"祝囡囡快樂成長，縱使未來成長的路未必平坦，但同你一樣依然係個善良有同理心的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（屌，最緊要有⻣氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"f7dd1bb4d0a00d2140b3ae88824650adbb41055e","tid":1762400,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"預產期係邊一日"}]}